# Massage Therapist Business Operations Platform - Detailed Implementation Tasks

## Project Vision
**A comprehensive iOS-native business management platform for massage therapists that handles EVERY aspect of running a massage practice - from clinical documentation to financial management to compliance tracking.**

---

